transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I have a question about the new AGV at Viagra. What's the price of that?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir. Price, yes. So there's three options.

Speaker 2: Forty pills, $149, $25, $99, and then $10 is $49.

Speaker 1: Well, I have an account. Can you pull me up and see if I'm still in there? It's been a lot of years.

Speaker 2: Yeah, we need your name and zip code.

Speaker 1: Bobby Barr, 37620.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Okey dokey, 386 Sinking Springs Road?

Speaker 2: Extension.

Speaker 1: Yep. Bristol, Tennessee, 37620?

Speaker 2: Yes, that's it.

Speaker 1: Okay, yeah. I do see that you ordered with us 2022, so yeah, it's been a little bit.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it's been a while. I would like to try the new one, but I don't want to do a whole bunch just in case it doesn't work like it.

Speaker 1: So you want to try the $10 to start?

Speaker 2: How much was the $10?

Speaker 1: That was the $49.

Speaker 2: And it was $100 for how many?

Speaker 1: $25.

Speaker 2: I'm sorry, I got confused. $25 for $100, right?

Speaker 1: Yeah, $25 pills is $99. $10 pills is $49. Everything comes with a money back guarantee.

Speaker 2: So if you're looking to get your better value, the $25 pills is going to be better value.

Speaker 1: And if it doesn't work, you can still get a refund on it.

Speaker 2: Okay, let's just try the $25 pills then.

Speaker 1: Okay, and you want to do 100 milligrams on those though?

Speaker 2: Yes, I do.

Speaker 1: That's no problem.

Speaker 2: Okay, whenever you're ready, I just need an updated card, sir.

Speaker 1: Okay, let me go over here. It should be – I know it's been changed since then.

Speaker 2: Okay, 4096291000005423.

Speaker 1: Thank you. Expiration?

Speaker 2: 127.

Speaker 1: And then the security code?

Speaker 2: 102.

Speaker 1: Okay, we're all set, Bobby.

Speaker 2: So what happens next is your prescription just gets renewed, and then we'll ship this out to you.

Speaker 1: I would expect it to get to you in about a week's time.

Speaker 2: Let us know how it goes, if that works out better for you than before.

Speaker 1: If you have any issues or questions, just call us.

Speaker 2: But you are all set and good to go.

Speaker 1: Could you give me the – did you get the extension on the address?

Speaker 2: Because if you don't, the extension won't show up.

Speaker 1: It is on there, yes. That is on there.

Speaker 2: I know I didn't say it, but it is on there.

Speaker 1: All right, I appreciate it.

Speaker 2: You're welcome.

Speaker 1: So that's exactly where it's going to be mailed out to.

Speaker 2: If you do have questions along the way, just call us.

Speaker 1: All right, thank you.

Speaker 2: Thanks, sir. Bye-bye.
